inating motherhood as a prestigious ideal to pursue is going to continue to=
 make society rot as a result.</span></p><p><span>But I guess this is the p=
roblem- we have a war between- I don=E2=80=99t want to judge you vs  you sh=
ould probably do more with your life than smoke weed all the time. The latt=
er is the most we can say, and it certainly isn=E2=80=99t an ideal. </span>=
